### Using the Data

#### Analyze with jq
```bash
# Extract all disk information
jq '.reconnaissance_data.block_devices' */raw_data.json

# Compare memory across hosts
jq -r '[.hostname, .ansible_facts.memtotal_mb] | @csv' */raw_data.json

# List all network interfaces
jq '.ansible_facts.interfaces' */raw_data.json
```

#### Search for specific hardware
```bash
# Find hosts with NVMe drives
grep -l nvme */disk_layout.md

# Find hosts with RAID
grep -l mdadm */system_report.md

# Check for specific network cards
grep -i mellanox */system_report.md
```

